      </svg>
      <p>
        <strong>In the notebook:</strong> Section 3 lets you explore tokenization
        hands-on&mdash;comparing how different models split the same text
        and observing multilingual tokenization inequality directly.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h3>Resources</h3>
    <ul class="resource-list">
